      <section class="mb-12">
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Artists, illustrators, and creative professionals in Malaysia who are relocating studios or exhibition spaces face unique packaging challenges. Canvases, paintings, sculpture materials, and specialized art supplies require careful protection. Used carton boxes offer a budget-conscious, eco-friendly solution that allows artists to focus on their craft rather than moving expenses.</p>
