        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Paint tubes, pigment bottles, and art solvents pack safely in medium used boxes (40x30x20cm) with cardboard dividers. This prevents bottles from rolling and breaking during transport. Clearly label contents to ensure safe handling.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Small Boxes for Brushes, Pencils & Fine Tools</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Artist brushes, specialized pencils, and sculpting tools are best organized in small used boxes with compartments. This prevents bristle damage and keeps tools inventory organized at your new studio location.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Clay, Sculptures & Delicate Materials</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Wrap sculptures individually in plastic wrap and bubble wrap. Pack in sturdy used boxes with crinkle fill or packing paper. Prevent shifting during transport to your new art studio in Balakong, Klang Valley, or across Peninsular Malaysia.</p>
